#. module: sale_shopee
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale_shopee.field_shopee_shop__status
msgid ""
"The shop status on Shopee.- Inactive: The shop is not yet approved by "
"Shopee.- Active: The shop is active and can be synchronized with Odoo.- "
"Error: The shop is banned and cannot be synchronized with Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Stav obchodu na Shopee.- Neaktívny: Obchod ešte nebol schválený platformou "
"Shopee.- Aktívny: Obchod je aktívny a je možné ho synchronizovať s Odoo.- "
"Chyba: Obchod bol zablokovaný a nie je možné ho synchronizovať s Odoo."

#. module: sale_shopee
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale_shopee.field_sale_order__shopee_delivery_status
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale_shopee.field_stock_picking__shopee_delivery_status
msgid ""
"The status of the delivery order on Shopee:\n"
"- Ready to Ship: Seller can arrange shipment.\n"
"- Shipment Arranged: Seller has arranged shipment online and got tracking "
"number from 3PL.\n"
"- Shipped: The parcel has been dropped at 3PL or picked up by 3PL.\n"
"- Cancelled: The order has been cancelled.\n"
"- Pickup Failed: 3PL parcel pickup failed. Need to rearrange shipment."
msgstr ""
"Stav dodacej objednávky na Shopee:\n"
"- Pripravené na odoslanie: Predajca môže zabezpečiť odoslanie.\n"
"- Odoslanie zabezpečené: Predajca zabezpečil odoslanie online a získal "
"sledovacie číslo od prepravcu.\n"
"- Odoslané: Balík bol odovzdaný spoločnosti prepravcu alebo vyzdvihnutý "
"prepravcom.\n"
"- Zrušené: Objednávka bola zrušená.\n"
"- Vyzdvihnutie sa nepodarilo: Vyzdvihnutie balíka spoločnosťou prepravcu sa "
"nepodarilo. Je potrebné zabezpečiť odoslanie nanovo."

#. module: sale_shopee
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:sale_shopee.field_stock_picking__shopee_label_status
msgid ""
"The status of the shipping label:\n"
"- Not Available: The shipping label is not available yet.\n"
"- Processing: The shipping label is being processed.\n"
"- Ready: The shipping label is ready to be downloaded.\n"
"- Stored: The shipping label has been downloaded and stored.\n"
"- Failed: The shipping label creation failed."
msgstr ""
"Stav prepravnej etikety:\n"
"- Nedostupné: Prepravná etiketa ešte nie je k dispozícii.\n"
"- Spracovanie: Prepravná etiketa sa práve spracováva.\n"
"- Pripravené: Prepravná etiketa je pripravená na stiahnutie.\n"
"- Uložené: Prepravná etiketa bola stiahnutá a uložená.\n"
"- Neúspešné: Vytvorenie prepravnej etikety sa nepodarilo."

